Rating: 3
My husband & I enjoyed this dish, however, we did make a few minor changes. First, I chopped the garlic. Whole garlic cloves don't thrilled me even if they've been braised for an hour and half. Second, we added the carrots the last 20 minutes of cooking. They were still tender and full of flavor, as opposed to the recipe calling them to be adding in the beginning, which would have left them over cooked. The sauce was delicious and cut through the heaviness of the lamb. Great over polenta!

